==制作==
该片由王岳伦担任导演和编剧，王岳伦妻子[[李湘_(主持人)|李湘]]担任制片人，李湘好友[[杜海涛|杜海涛]]友情客串。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.ifeng.com/movie/news/mainland/detail_2012_07/09/15878608_0.shtml|title=《乐翻天》8月2日上映 李湘：票房不超5千万卖火锅|date=2012-07-09|accessdate=2014-03-16|work=凤凰网|archive-date=2019-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719043524/http://ent.ifeng.com/movie/news/mainland/detail_2012_07/09/15878608_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

该片中，宁静的服饰成为最大亮点，“高发髻、低胸豹纹、黑色短裙”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/ent/2012-08/07/c_123544168.htm|title=宁静成“妖孽”女人 《乐翻天》上演制服诱惑(图)|date=2012-08-07|accessdate=2014-03-16|work=新华网|archive-date=2014-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407212814/http://news.xinhuanet.com/ent/2012-08/07/c_123544168.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.163.com/12/0807/09/88A0NKUG000300B1.html|title=宁静《乐翻天》成“妖孽”女人 上演制服诱惑|date=2012-08-07|accessdate=2014-03-16|work=网易|archive-date=2020-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815024125/http://ent.163.com/12/0807/09/88A0NKUG000300B1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

该片得到李湘老东家[[湖南卫视|湖南卫视]]官方网的赞誉。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hunantv.com/c/20120802/1541035296.html |title=平均两分钟一个笑点 《乐翻天》宁静大秀事业线 |date=2012-08-02 |accessdate=2014-03-16 |work=金鹰网 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924032008/http://www.hunantv.com/c/20120802/1541035296.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

